    EuclideanMapView
    A set of functions used by the environment and the grid domain All of them will evaluated the grid domain to a Euclidean grid map Thus diagonal travel is valid

    GridEnviron
    Encapsulate all data relavent to the execution of an agent on a grid map Contains the map, the planner, start position and goal position and all data collected from the planner Also fires event on certain condition with the IGridEnvironUpdateListener This serves as the main entry point for the model
    ManhattanMapView
    A set of functions used by the environment and the grid domain All of them will evaluated the grid domain to a Manhatten grid map Thus only left, right, up, down is valid
